{"type": "article", "id": 9320, "title": "Vanquish City 地毯", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-08T07:22:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235126p82vNQOg4x7Tsatw.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t日本街头品牌 Vanquish 旗下的 Vanquish City 支线最近推出了两款地毯。这两款地毯专门为单身人士设计，其中，白色方形地毯上写着 “Hello！” 字样，而咖啡色的对话气泡形状地毯则有一句大胆的 “Can I Take You?” 除了有趣的造型，地毯还进行了降噪设计，目前售价是 12960 日元（约合 673 元人民币），这是<a href=\"http://vanquish.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">官方购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235123M817NnLleP5CfKXZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;white-space:normal;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235123TFqVOvykwtaMzYul.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235124oHDqCKQrBsN7tp8F.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235124RYE8dgTJA4rtHfXm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052351257P2UIiCDfLqzM1H6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235125CVWvbXlOhsmPNI4H.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}